# nexus

## Run

- `nexus kick <topic>` — fire ω-cycle (모든 default 자동: parent_sid 합성, axes, noise, backend)
- `nexus kick status` — hosts/slot pool/cache 1-view 진단
- `nexus kick tree` — registry (axes/strata/backends/noise)
- `nexus kick bench <topic> --backends a,b,c` — cross-backend perf
- `nexus omega --seed "..."` — L_ω apex drill
- `nexus atlas search "..."` — atlas.n6 검색
- `nexus roadmap` — phase 조회
- `nexus doctor` — 통합 진단

Witness: `design/kick/<YYYY-MM-DD>_<topic-slug>_omega_cycle.json`

## Files (root SSOT)

| path | role |
|---|---|
| `.own` | nexus L1 룰 (atlas-absorb-mandatory) |
| `.guide` | this file |
| `.roadmap` | phase + meta-engine track |
| `.ext .turn .end .command .meta .chain` | derived SSOT (locked uchg) |
| `~/core/hive/.raw` | L0 universal (44 rules) |
| `~/core/.workspace` | super-bundle topology + member exports |
| `cli/run.hexa` | subcommand dispatch SSOT (직접 호출 금지) |
| `n6/atlas.n6` | symlink to n6-architecture canonical (READ + APPEND only) |

## Conventions

- **claude-dependency=0, hooks=0** — no PreToolUse/PostToolUse, no .git/hooks, no fswatch
- **canonical witness path** — `tool/witness_emit.hexa` 만 — 직접 JSON write = orphan
- **atlas.signals.n6 / atlas.millennium.n6 NEVER edit** — main atlas 만 absorb 대상
- **새 .py / .sh / .rs / .toml 추가 금지** — hexa-only (raw#9, 기존 grandfathered)
- **direct invocation 금지** — `hexa run cli/run.hexa kick` 등 우회 금지. `nexus kick` shim 만 사용. shim 부재 시 `nx install` 재설치

